---
title: Italian Chicken & Lemon Risotto with Garlic Pangrattato & Pear Salad
description: Enjoy all the flavours of a rich and creamy risotto, without standing over the stove for too long! With tender chicken, spinach and zesty lemon, this mouth-watering meal will be happily devoured by all.
